            <p>Patient disposition. ICS, inhaled corticosteroid; FP/S, fluticasone propionate/salmeterol combination; MF/F, mometasone furoate/formoterol. &#x2018;Patient population used for safety analyses. tPatient population used for efficacy analyses, identified before database lock.</p>
